title: Dana Kellin Dark Silver Crystal Geo Layer Necklace
description:
Swarovski Crystal Dark Silver Shade surrounding clear Crystals Geo diamond shapes with metal beads on oxidized sterling silver chain. 14k gold fill wire wrap detail. Each piece is constructed by wrapping fine-gauge sterling silver, gold fill and 14K gold wire with precious, semi-precious and pearl stones and metal beads into various sculptural formations.
